items.title: 25% discount on your first 4 food boxes from Adams Matkasse
items.excerpt: Exciting dinners every day with local ingredients of high quality
items.description: Adams Matkasse makes it easier to gather around the dinner table and eat dinner favorites with good ingredients. Whether you let the chefs choose the menu for you, or you choose the dinner dishes yourself, you get the best ingredients straight home. Each week, the food box is delivered with tempting dinner recipes, made by Adam's cooking team. The recipes are easy to use, and the ingredients are carefully selected from local small producers in Norway.

items.title: Health Test - Intolerance test against over 750 foods, 80 nutrients and 50 metals
items.excerpt: Tired, lethargic, stomach ache, nausea? Test yourself for intolerance and hypersensitivity
items.description: Do you feel tired most of the day, or do you get a huge stomach ache when you eat cream cake? With the Health Diagnostics intolerance test, you can test yourself for 750 different foods and non-foods. For example, you can find out if you are gluten intolerant or lactose intolerant and if you have nutritional deficiencies, such as zinc, magnesium and vitamin D.
